MyBroadband’s 2016 Technology Survey has revealed that Samsung is the favourite smartphone and tablet brand of South African techies. The survey was completed by 2,134 respondents, of which 64% were either an IT professional, IT manager, or general techie. Respondents were asked an array of questions, including what their favourite smartphone and tablet brands were. In the mobile processor category, Qualcomm took top spot. The graphic below details the results of the 2016 Technology Survey. 